---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Nitro Sport Gym · Gimnasio en Brisas del Bosque, Mérida"
  description="⭐ 4.4 con 151 reseñas en Google. Máquinas completas, un coach que te ayuda de verdad y un ambiente donde te vas a sentir cómodo desde el día uno. Escríbenos por WhatsApp."
  slug="nitro-sport-gym"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
  favicon="⚡"
  themeColor="#12151b"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/529994104178"}
  telefono={"999 410 4178"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=14695277351621915599&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <main class="ns">

    <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="streaks" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="wrap hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <p class="kicker reveal">Gimnasio · Brisas del Bosque, Mérida</p>
          <h1 class="poster reveal">
            <span class="l1">NITRO</span>
            <span class="l2">SPORT GYM</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="tagline reveal">Máquinas completas, un coach que te ayuda de verdad y un ambiente donde te vas a sentir <strong>cómodo desde el día uno</strong>.</p>

          <a class="chip reveal" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=14695277351621915599&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.4 · 151 reseñas en Google
          </a>

          <div class="cta-row reveal">
            <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://wa.me/529994104178" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2zm0 18.2c-1.5 0-3-.4-4.3-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1-.2.3-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-3.4-3c-.3-.4 0-.5.2-.7l.4-.5c.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5v-.5c0-.1-.5-1.3-.7-1.8-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.3.3-.9.9-.9 2.2s.9 2.5 1 2.7c.1.2 1.8 2.8 4.4 3.9.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.6.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2l-.4-.3z"/></svg>
              Escríbenos por WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=14695277351621915599&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.2 7 13 7 13s7-7.8 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7zm0 9.5A2.5 2.5 0 1 1 12 6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5z"/></svg>
              Cómo llegar
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ELEMENTO FIRMA: medidor NITRO -->
        <div class="gauge-wrap reveal">
          <svg class="gauge-svg" viewBox="0 0 240 140" role="img" aria-label="Medidor NITRO: 4.4 de 5, dentro de la zona NITRO">
            <path class="zone zone-idle" d="M20,120 A100,100 0 0 1 70,33.40" />
            <path class="zone zone-ritmo" d="M70,33.40 A100,100 0 0 1 170,33.40" />
            <path class="zone zone-nitro" d="M170,33.40 A100,100 0 0 1 220,120" />
            <line class="tick" x1="18" y1="120" x2="6" y2="120" />
            <line class="tick" x1="47.87" y1="47.87" x2="39.39" y2="39.39" />
            <line class="tick" x1="120" y1="18" x2="120" y2="6" />
            <line class="tick" x1="192.13" y1="47.87" x2="200.61" y2="39.39" />
            <line class="tick" x1="222" y1="120" x2="234" y2="120" />
            <g class="needle-group">
              <line class="needle" x1="120" y1="120" x2="192.5" y2="86.2" />
              <circle class="hub" cx="120" cy="120" r="9" />
            </g>
          </svg>
          <div class="gauge-labels" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>Idle</span><span>Ritmo</span><span class="nitro-label">Nitro</span>
          </div>
          <div class="gauge-readout">
            <span class="readout-num">4.4</span>
            <span class="readout-sub">★ 151 reseñas en Google</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Firma secundaria: bandera a cuadros con ticker -->
    <div class="flagband" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="flag">
        <div class="flag-track">
          <span>Pesas · Cardio · Coaching · Constancia · Buen ambiente ·&nbsp;</span>
          <span>Pesas · Cardio · Coaching · Constancia · Buen ambiente ·&nbsp;</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ 01 QUIÉNES SOMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="nosotros">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">01 / Quiénes somos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Aquí agarras <span class="accent">ritmo</span></h2>
        <div class="about reveal">
          <p>Somos <strong>NITRO SPORT GYM</strong>, un gimnasio en Brisas del Bosque, al norte de Mérida. Aquí no hay filas eternas para las máquinas ni miradas raras si es tu primera semana entrenando: el objetivo es que agarres ritmo y no lo sueltes.</p>
          <p>Eso es justo lo que más repiten quienes ya entrenan con nosotros: lo amable que es el equipo, lo cómodo que se siente el ambiente desde el primer día y lo completo que está el área de maquinaria. Nuestro coach Tito es de los que explican, corrigen y te ayudan muchísimo — no te deja solo con las pesas.</p>
          <p>Si venías posponiendo eso de «empezar el gym», este es el lugar para hacerlo sin sentirte fuera de lugar. Con estacionamiento disponible, para que la única excusa que te falte sea esa.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 02 INSTALACIONES ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="instalaciones">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">02 / Instalaciones</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Lo que vas a encontrar</h2>
        <div class="panels reveal">
          <div class="panel-card">
            <span class="panel-num">01</span>
            <h3>Maquinaria completa</h3>
            <p>Suficiente equipo para que no te quedes esperando turno: área bien surtida para entrenar en serio.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-card">
            <span class="panel-num">02</span>
            <h3>Coaching que sí te acompaña</h3>
            <p>El coach Tito corrige tu técnica y te ayuda muchísimo, no solo prende el cronómetro.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-card">
            <span class="panel-num">03</span>
            <h3>Ambiente sin intimidación</h3>
            <p>El tipo de gym donde te sientes cómodo aunque sea tu primera semana — así lo describen quienes ya entrenan aquí.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-card">
            <span class="panel-num">04</span>
            <h3>Estacionamiento disponible</h3>
            <p>Para que llegar a entrenar no sea la parte difícil del día.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 03 PRUEBA SOCIAL ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="resenas">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">03 / Lo que dicen</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal"><span class="accent">4.4</span> de 5 en <span class="accent">151</span> reseñas de Google</h2>
        <figure class="rev reveal">
          <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
          <blockquote>«Acabo de inscribirme y es increíble lo amables que son y lo cómodo que se siente. La gente es muy amable y está bastante completo en cuanto a maquinaria y el coach Tito es amable y te ayuda muchísimo. Estoy contento de iniciar esta vida fit jejejej»</blockquote>
          <figcaption><strong>Ricardo Antonio Suarez Hidalgo</strong><span>Hace 6 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="center reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=14695277351621915599&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 04 UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">04 / Dónde estamos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Brisas del Bosque, Mérida</h2>
        <div class="ubica reveal">
          <div class="ubica-info">
            <p class="dir">C. 29 478, Brisas del Bosque<br />97144 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
            <a class="btn btn-solid btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=14695277351621915599&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en Google Maps</a>
            <h3 class="horario-titulo">Horario</h3>
            <table class="horarios">
              <tbody>
                <tr data-dia="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>6:00–22:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>8:00–13:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="mapa">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=NITRO%20SPORT%20GYM%2C%20C.%2029%20478%2C%20Brisas%20del%20Bosque%2C%2097144%20M%C3%A9rida%2C%20Yuc.%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
              title="Mapa: Nitro Sport Gym en Brisas del Bosque, Mérida"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="banda">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="banda-title">¿Listo para tu primer Nitro?</h2>
        <p class="banda-sub">Escríbenos y arrancamos — sin vueltas, sin excusas.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/529994104178" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp directo</a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark-ghost" href="tel:+529994104178">Llamar · 999 410 4178</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="pie">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="pie-logo">Nitro Sport Gym</p>
        <p class="pie-dato">Gimnasio · C. 29 478, Brisas del Bosque, 97144 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
        <p class="pie-dato"><a href="tel:+529994104178">999 410 4178</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/529994104178" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a></p>
        <p class="pie-mini">Lunes a viernes 6:00–22:00 · Sábado 8:00–13:00 · Domingo cerrado</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HealthClub",
    "name": "NITRO SPORT GYM",
    "telephone": "+529994104178",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/nitro-sport-gym",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "C. 29 478, Brisas del Bosque",
      "addressLocality": "Mérida",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97144",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.4",
      "reviewCount": "151"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Fr 06:00-22:00", "Sa 08:00-13:00"]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --ink: #12151b;
      --panel: #181c25;
      --cyan: #22d3ee;
      --orange: #f97316;
      --steel: #cbd5e1;
      --muted: #8a94a6;
      --line: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.14);
      --display: "Orbitron", "Arial Narrow", sans-serif;
      --body: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background:
        radial-gradient(900px 520px at 88% -6%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.12), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(700px 480px at 8% 108%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.10), transparent 55%),
        var(--ink);
      color: var(--steel);
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .ns ::selection { background: var(--cyan); color: var(--ink); }
    .ns a:focus-visible,
    .ns .btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--cyan);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 38px);
      min-height: calc(100svh - 38px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 36px;
      padding: 56px 0 40px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background-image:
        repeating-linear-gradient(115deg, rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.05) 0 1px, transparent 1px 7px);
      background-position: 0 0;
    }
    .streaks {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(100deg, transparent 46%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.14) 48%, transparent 51%),
        linear-gradient(100deg, transparent 61%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.10) 63%, transparent 66%);
      background-size: 220% 100%;
      animation: streakmove 9s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    @keyframes streakmove {
      0% { background-position: 0 0, 0 0; }
      100% { background-position: -220% 0, -180% 0; }
    }
    .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .hero-text { max-width: 640px; }
    .kicker {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }
    .poster {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--display);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 0.92;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .poster .l1 {
      font-size: clamp(52px, 17vw, 132px);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      background: linear-gradient(100deg, var(--cyan) 15%, var(--orange) 92%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      color: var(--cyan);
    }
    .poster .l2 {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 5.4vw, 34px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: transparent;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 1.4px var(--steel);
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    @supports not (-webkit-text-stroke: 1px black) {
      .poster .l2 { color: var(--steel); }
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(17px, 4.4vw, 22px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--steel);
      max-width: 36ch;
      margin: 22px 0 16px;
    }
    .tagline strong { color: var(--cyan); font-weight: 600; }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--steel);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.04);
    }
    .chip .star { color: var(--orange); }
    .chip:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); }

    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin: 24px 0 0; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--cyan); color: var(--ink); }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: #5fe4f7; }
    .btn-ghost { border: 2px solid var(--line); color: var(--steel); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--cyan); }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 18px; }

    /* ---------- GAUGE (firma) ---------- */
    .gauge-wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .gauge-svg { width: min(88vw, 300px); height: auto; overflow: visible; }
    .zone { fill: none; stroke-width: 16; stroke-linecap: round; }
    .zone-idle { stroke: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.22); }
    .zone-ritmo { stroke: var(--cyan); }
    .zone-nitro { stroke: var(--orange); }
    .tick { stroke: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.4); stroke-width: 2; }
    .needle-group {
      transform-origin: 120px 120px;
      animation: rev 1.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 1;
    }
    .needle { stroke: var(--steel); stroke-width: 4; stroke-linecap: round; }
    .hub { fill: var(--steel); }
    @keyframes rev {
      0% { transform: rotate(-58deg); }
      65% { transform: rotate(6deg); }
      100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    }
    .gauge-labels {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      width: min(88vw, 300px);
      margin-top: -18px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .nitro-label { color: var(--orange); }
    .gauge-readout {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .readout-num {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 8vw, 42px);
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .readout-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ---------- FLAGBAND (firma secundaria) ---------- */
    .flagband { overflow: hidden; padding: 14px 0; }
    .flag {
      transform: rotate(-1.4deg);
      width: 106%;
      margin-left: -3%;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      background-color: #e9edf3;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(45deg, #12151b 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, #12151b 75%, #12151b),
        linear-gradient(45deg, #12151b 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, #12151b 75%, #12151b);
      background-size: 22px 22px;
      background-position: 0 0, 11px 11px;
    }
    .flag-track {
      display: inline-flex;
      white-space: nowrap;
      animation: flagmove 20s linear infinite;
      background: rgba(18, 21, 27, 0.86);
    }
    .flag-track span {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      padding: 11px 0;
    }
    @keyframes flagmove { to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

    /* ---------- SECCIONES ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 76px 0; }
    .sec-panel { background: var(--panel); }
    .sec-kicker {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 7.6vw, 56px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      color: var(--steel);
    }
    .sec-title .accent { color: var(--orange); }

    .about p { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 0 18px; color: var(--steel); }
    .about strong { color: var(--cyan); }

    /* ---------- INSTALACIONES ---------- */
    .panels {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .panel-card {
      position: relative;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 22px 20px 20px;
      background: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.03);
    }
    .panel-card::before,
    .panel-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-color: var(--cyan);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    .panel-card::before {
      top: -1px; left: -1px;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--cyan);
      border-left: 2px solid var(--cyan);
    }
    .panel-card::after {
      bottom: -1px; right: -1px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--orange);
      border-right: 2px solid var(--orange);
    }
    .panel-num {
      display: block;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--orange);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .panel-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      color: var(--steel);
    }
    .panel-card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }

    /* ---------- RESEÑAS ---------- */
    .rev {
      margin: 0 0 30px;
      max-width: 640px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px 24px 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    }
    .rev-stars { color: var(--orange); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin: 0 0 12px; }
    .rev blockquote {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--steel);
    }
    .rev figcaption { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
    .rev figcaption strong {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--cyan);
    }
    .rev figcaption span { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
    .center { text-align: center; }

    /* ---------- UBICACIÓN ---------- */
    .ubica { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .dir { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--steel); }
    .horario-titulo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 30px 0 10px;
      color: var(--steel);
    }
    .horarios { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15.5px; }
    .horarios th, .horarios td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
    .horarios th { font-weight: 500; color: var(--steel); }
    .horarios td { color: var(--muted); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th, .horarios tr.hoy td { color: var(--ink); background: var(--cyan); font-weight: 600; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th::after {
      content: "hoy";
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--cyan);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-left: 10px;
      vertical-align: 1px;
    }
    .mapa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: block;
      filter: invert(90%) contrast(0.9) brightness(0.95) hue-rotate(180deg);
    }

    /* ---------- CTA FINAL ---------- */
    .banda {
      background: linear-gradient(100deg, var(--cyan) 0%, var(--orange) 100%);
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 64px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .banda-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 7.6vw, 50px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .banda-sub { margin: 0 auto 24px; max-width: 42ch; font-weight: 500; }
    .banda .cta-row { justify-content: center; }
    .btn-dark { background: var(--ink); color: var(--steel); }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: #23293a; }
    .btn-dark-ghost { border: 2px solid rgba(18, 21, 27, 0.6); color: var(--ink); }
    .btn-dark-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .pie {
      padding: 44px 0 96px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .pie-logo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--steel);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .pie-dato { margin: 4px 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; }
    .pie-dato a { color: var(--cyan); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4); }
    .pie-dato a:hover { color: var(--orange); border-color: var(--orange); }
    .pie-mini { margin: 14px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12.5px; }

    /* ---------- REVEAL (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- DESKTOP ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .sec { padding: 110px 0; }
      .panels { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .ubica { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; align-items: start; }
      .mapa iframe { height: 420px; }
      .flag-track span { font-size: 22px; }
      .hero-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 32px; }
      .gauge-wrap { flex-shrink: 0; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var d = document;
      d.documentElement.classList.add('js');

      // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
      var hoy = new Date().getDay(); // 0 = domingo
      var fila = d.querySelector('.horarios tr[data-dia="' + hoy + '"]');
      if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

      // Scroll-reveal (mejora progresiva)
      var els = d.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        els.forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      } else {
        els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
